summary: My very first mod for skyrim, ive made a new player home for the player who likes magic and want a cozy fortress with an evil touch ;-)
descriptionHtml:
My very first mod for skyrim, ive made a new player home for the player who likes magic and want a cozy old fortress with an evil touch ;-)

Dovahkiins Warlock Fortress is located in Alftand (Just TP to Alftand and turn around;)

**UPDATED RELEASE ADDED!** (Fixed alot off bugs and added new stuff, i have also changed the exterior of the fortress, it looks much better now with 4 new big \"towers\" and 2 big mage statues guarding the fortress entrance!

Features:

There is a total off 14 rooms, complete with furniture and details, several bedrooms etc.

All major workbenches in the game is added

4 Main levels: First Floor, Second Floor, Third Floor and Fourth Floor

First Floor is: Fortress Entrance and big hall, a throne and kitchen and small magic enchanting room.

Second Floor is: Bedroom, relaxing room, two crafting rooms and small enchanting and potion making room.

Third Floor is: Guest Bedrooms, mannequin room, crafting room and master bedroom

Fourth Floor is: Tower Armory, Lots of crafting benches and weapon racks, shield racks and chests is located in the Fortress Tower

Updates (objects, items etc.) to my Fortress will be added in future release.
author: DarkIncLegion and VelociraptorGTX
